<% content_for :title, "Team" %>
<div class="fullRow teamWideBlurred">
	<div class="absoluteHero">
		<h1>We're a rag-tag team of dragon slayers...</h1>
		<p class="largerParagraph">Poliana is made up of developers, designers, and entrepreneurs on a mission to clear up the political landscape.</p>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="row teamMember extraPad">
	<div class="large-3 small-6 small-centered large-uncentered columns">
		<%= image_tag "pictures/grayson.jpg", :alt => "Grayson Carroll" %>
	</div>
	<div class="large-9 columns">
		<ul class="inline-list">
			<li><h3>Grayson Carroll</h3></li>
			<li><%= link_to "<span aria-hidden='true' class='icon-linkedin'></span>".html_safe, "http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=257513776", :target => "_blank" %></li>
			<li><%= link_to "<span aria-hidden='true' class='icon-envelop'></span>".html_safe, "mailto:grayson@poliana.com", :target => "_blank" %></li>
		</ul>
		<p>The brains of the whole operation would be none other than that of Grayson Carroll. He has worked as a full-stack web programmer and is currently wrapping up a Computer Science degree. Grayson has been a political enthusiast since the womb and has a long-sought vision for political transparency and a more effective America.</p>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="row teamMember extraPad">
	<div class="large-3 small-6 small-centered large-uncentered columns">
		<%= image_tag "pictures/patrick.jpg", :alt => "Patrick Cason" %>
	</div>
	<div class="large-9 columns">
		<ul class="inline-list">
			<li><h3>Patrick Cason</h3></li>
			<li><%= link_to "<span aria-hidden='true' class='icon-twitter'></span>".html_safe, "https://www.twitter.com/cereallarceny", :target => "_blank" %></li>
			<li><%= link_to "<span aria-hidden='true' class='icon-linkedin'></span>".html_safe, "http://www.linkedin.com/in/patrickcason", :target => "_blank" %></li>
			<li><%= link_to "<span aria-hidden='true' class='icon-envelop'></span>".html_safe, "mailto:patrick@poliana.com", :target => "_blank" %></li>
		</ul>
		<p>While appearing as a web designer and developer on the outside, Patrick has the entrepreneurial spirit of a fierce Siberian tiger. Patrick has spent most of his time as a freelancer, while also working at a design firm along the way. As he earns a degree in Web Development, Patrick uses his free-time repairing and playing vintage keyboards and organs while also designing pretty graphs for Poliana.</p>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="row teamMember extraPad">
	<div class="large-3 small-6 small-centered large-uncentered columns">
		<%= image_tag "pictures/david.jpg", :alt => "David Gilmore" %>
	</div>
	<div class="large-9 columns">
		<ul class="inline-list">
			<li><h3>David Gilmore</h3></li>
			<li><%= link_to "<span aria-hidden='true' class='icon-linkedin'></span>".html_safe, "http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=114293672", :target => "_blank" %></li>
			<li><%= link_to "<span aria-hidden='true' class='icon-envelop'></span>".html_safe, "mailto:david@poliana.com", :target => "_blank" %></li>
		</ul>
		<p>Like any true nerd, David lives in a world where semi-colons are his alphabet soup and data reigns supreme over the lands. While working on a bachelors degree in Computer Science, he spends all his free-time playing drums and coding on Poliana. David also worked at <%= link_to "Emma", "https://myemma.com", :target => "_blank" %> as a back-end engineer, and frequently enjoys a nice glass of aged Scotch; he’s the definition of a true gentleman.</p>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="row teamMember extraPad">
	<div class="large-3 small-6 small-centered large-uncentered columns">
		<%= image_tag "pictures/shawn.jpg", :alt => "Shawn Whiting" %>
	</div>
	<div class="large-9 columns">
		<ul class="inline-list">
			<li><h3>Shawn Whiting</h3></li>
			<li><%= link_to "<span aria-hidden='true' class='icon-linkedin'></span>".html_safe, "http://www.linkedin.com/in/shawnwhiting", :target => "_blank" %></li>
			<li><%= link_to "<span aria-hidden='true' class='icon-envelop'></span>".html_safe, "mailto:shawn@poliana.com", :target => "_blank" %></li>
		</ul>
