	</div>
</div>
<div class="row hero">
	<div class="large-12 columns">
		<h2>Passionate about political transparency?</h2>
		<p><%= link_to "Send us an email", contact_path %>, we’d love to see what you can bring to the table.</p>
	</div>
</div>